<div><head>《陳子要言》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1466_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1466_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1466_CHANT_001-1a.2">食穀而鄙田，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1466_CHANT_001-1a.3">衣帛而笑蠶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1466_CHANT_001-1a.4">是惑也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1466_CHANT_001-1a.5">《太平御覽》卷八百三十七。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1466_CHANT_001-1a.6">棄晨雞犬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1466_CHANT_001-1a.7">候鳳驚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1466_CHANT_001-1a.8">亦猶棄當世之實才，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1466_CHANT_001-1a.9">須故人之執政也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1466_CHANT_001-1a.10">《太平御覽》卷九百一十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
